node.text:
Tailgater or Tail-GATOR? 
Whether you’re Florida Man or Football Fan, you’d have to agree: the passion, fellowship and fantastic food I got to experience at The University of Florida with #TailgateNation was second to none and needs to be seen to be believed! 
We know there are a lot of amazing tailgate experiences all over the country and we’re gearing up for next season so… 📢 Comment with the tailgates and schools you want us to visit next year!!! Thank you to all the fans, all the schools, and everyone who let us share in their passion for an incredible first season and journey with @GeneralMills and #TailgateNation! #ad
